<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.pcworld.com/article/110841/pgp_encryption_proves_powerful.html" class="external free" title="http://www.pcworld.com/article/110841/pgp_encryption_proves_powerful.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.pcworld.com/article/110841/pgp_encryption_proves_powerful.html</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.news.com/8301-13578_3-9834495-38.html?tag=nefd.blgs" class="external text" title="http://www.news.com/8301-13578_3-9834495-38.html?tag=nefd.blgs" rel="nofollow">Judge: Man can't be forced to divulge encryption passphrase | The Iconoclast - politics, law, and technology - CNET News.com</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.news.com/8301-13578_3-9854034-38.html" class="external text" title="http://www.news.com/8301-13578_3-9854034-38.html" rel="nofollow">Feds appeal loss in PGP compelled-passphrase case | The Iconoclast - politics, law, and technology - CNET News.com</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://news.cnet.com/8301-13578_3-10172866-38.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://news.cnet.com/8301-13578_3-10172866-38.html" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/11/14/ripa_encryption_key_notice" class="external free" title="http://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/11/14/ripa_encryption_key_notice" rel="nofollow">http://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/11/14/ripa_encryption_key_notice</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-zimmermann2-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-zimmermann2_9-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFZimmermann1995"><a href="/wiki/Philip_Zimmermann" title="Philip Zimmermann" class="mw-redirect">Zimmermann, Philip</a> (1995). <i>PGP Source Code and Internals</i>. <a href="/wiki/MIT_Press" title="MIT Press">MIT Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0262240394" class="internal">ISBN 0-262-24039-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=PGP+Source+Code+and+Internals&amp;rft.aulast=Zimmermann&amp;rft.aufirst=Philip&amp;rft.au=Zimmermann%2C+Philip&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BMIT+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0-262-24039-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Pretty_Good_Privacy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
