<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Pretty_Good_Privacy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<p><a name="OpenPGP_implementations" id="OpenPGP_implementations"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Pretty_Good_Privacy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: OpenPGP implementations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">OpenPGP implementations</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.pgp.com" class="external text" title="http://www.pgp.com" rel="nofollow">PGP Corporation</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.gnupg.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.gnupg.org/" rel="nofollow">GNU Privacy Guard</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cgeep.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.cgeep.com/" rel="nofollow">cGeep Pro</a></li>
<li><a href="http://openpgp.nominet.org.uk/" class="external text" title="http://openpgp.nominet.org.uk/" rel="nofollow">OpenPGP::SDK</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.authora.com" class="external text" title="http://www.authora.com" rel="nofollow">Authora Inc.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.mcafee.com/us/products/mcafee/encryption/category.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.mcafee.com/us/products/mcafee/encryption/category.htm" rel="nofollow">McAfee Inc.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.feneris.com" class="external text" title="http://www.feneris.com" rel="nofollow">Feneris Solutions Inc. Canada</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.easybyte.com/products/cryptocx.html" class="external text" title="http://www.easybyte.com/products/cryptocx.html" rel="nofollow">EasyByte Cryptocx</a> - Component</li>
<li><a href="http://www.veridis.com/openpgp/en/index.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.veridis.com/openpgp/en/index.asp" rel="nofollow">Veridis</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bouncycastle.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.bouncycastle.org/" rel="nofollow">Legion of The Bouncy Castle</a></li>
<li><a href="http://netbsd-soc.sourceforge.net/projects/bpg/" class="external text" title="http://netbsd-soc.sourceforge.net/projects/bpg/" rel="nofollow">BSD Privacy Guard</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.primefactors.com/what_psypherOPS.html" class="external text" title="http://www.primefactors.com/what_psypherOPS.html" rel="nofollow">Prime Factors Inc.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://secemail.brookes.ac.uk/" class="external text" title="http://secemail.brookes.ac.uk/" rel="nofollow">Oxford Brookes Secure Email Proxy</a></li>
